# Veterans of Foreign Wars: 2024 Telehealth Experience Survey Report

**Prepared by:** VFW National Veterans Service
**Survey Period:** April - June 2024
**Respondents:** 3,247 VFW members who used VA telehealth services
**Report Date:** August 2024

---

## Executive Summary

The Veterans of Foreign Wars conducted a comprehensive survey of members' experiences with VA telehealth services to inform our advocacy priorities and provide actionable feedback to VA leadership. This report presents key findings and recommendations based on responses from over 3,200 Veterans across all 50 states.

**Key Takeaways:**
- 78% of respondents value telehealth and want to continue using it
- 61% experienced technical difficulties at least once
- 44% needed help from family member or caregiver to connect
- 89% want easier ways to test their setup before appointments
- Veterans over 70 report 2x more technical challenges than younger Veterans

